Hello! Thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers technical support. My name is Matthew Long. How can I assist you today?

Hi, thanks for helping. I'm having a little trouble with the online portal.

I’d be happy to help with that. May I start by getting your name, please?

Of course! My name is Hannah Griffin.

Thank you, Hannah. Could I please confirm your email address to look up your account?

Sure, my email address is hannah.griffin@example.com.

Got it, thank you. One more thing, I will need the last four digits of your customer ID.

The last four digits are two two six five.

Great, I have everything I need. I see the issue and will have it resolved shortly. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all. Thanks for your help, Matthew.

You're welcome, Hannah. Thank you for your time and for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a great day!
